<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page d'Accueil</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff !important;
        }
        .nav-link {
            color: #333 !important;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            color: #007bff !important;
        }

        /* Sections */
        .hero-section, .second-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 50px;
            min-height: 90vh;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: white;
            background: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        .image-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-section, .second-section {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .content {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            .image-container img {
                width: 80%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">UAP Immo</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Accueil</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Nos Services</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary me-3">Se connecter</a>
                    <select class="form-select">
                        <option value="fr">FR</option>
                        <option value="en">EN</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Penser durablement et stratégiquement !</h1>
                <p>Faites la différence face à la concurrence. Investissez dans l’avenir et soyez compétitif dès aujourd’hui.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">En savoir plus</a>
            </div>
            <div class="image-container">
                <img src="image1.png" alt="Illustration Business">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <section class="second-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="image-container">
                <img src="image2.png" alt="Illustration Business 2">
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Optimisez votre performance digitale</h1>
                <p>Développez votre présence en ligne et améliorez votre visibilité grâce à des stratégies digitales efficaces.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Découvrir nos services</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <p>© 2024 UAP Immo. Tous droits réservés.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="#">Mentions Légales</a> |
                <a href="#">Politique de Confidentialité</a> |
                <a href="#">Contact</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
